# Project Rules

This project is Graceward: Daily Reflection.

Graceward is a private Christian reflection app.

## Non-Negotiables

- iOS-first
- Expo + React Native + TypeScript
- Local-first
- Privacy-conscious
- Scripture-rooted
- AI through backend only
- No secrets in frontend
- No raw journal content in analytics
- No cloud-first private data unless explicitly designed
- Update docs when changing architecture

## Product Positioning

Graceward helps users process their day through voice or text, turning thoughts into prayer points, gratitude, biblical reflection, and reminders of God's faithfulness.
